Great news – we’ve added a new feature to make it even easier to update your property photos on the go. 

We also fixed those annoying bugs that interfered with your everyday use of the app. 

Here are the new features to try out...

-Upload and edit your property photos
-Adjust the minimum length of stay for your rooms
-Sort your list of upcoming bookings
